  "body": "In the current implementation the approved operator can not send tokens.\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/OpenZeppelin/openzeppelin-contracts/blob/fb36326a58f1bf05896014d540ba7190886e5673/contracts/token/ERC721/ERC721.sol#L334\r\n\r\nOn this line sender is required to be a token owner, while on the \r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/OpenZeppelin/openzeppelin-contracts/blob/fb36326a58f1bf05896014d540ba7190886e5673/contracts/token/ERC721/ERC721.sol#L158\r\n\r\nline it allows sender to be just approved also.",
